OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1780095786
OL,3,CDrone hits Romanian apartment block as
OL,4,CNato condemns Russia's 'recklessness'
OL,6,FWatch: Emergency services at the scene
OL,7,Fin Galati, Romania, after a Russian
OL,8,Fdrone struck an apartment building
OL,10,FA Russian drone has hit an apartment
OL,11,Fbuilding in Romania, injuring two
OL,12,Fpeople, in an incident that the head
OL,13,Fof Nato condemned as "reckless".
OL,15,FThe roof of the building in Galati,
OL,16,Fwhich lies near the southeastern
OL,17,Fborder with Ukraine, was left visibly
OL,18,Fcharred, with debris seen scattered on
OL,19,Fthe ground below.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1780095786
OL,3,CDrone hits Romanian apartment block as
OL,4,CNato condemns Russia's 'recklessness'
OL,6,FThe drone entered the country's
OL,7,Fairspace shortly before 2am on Friday,
OL,8,Faccording to Romania's defence
OL,9,Fministry - around the same time
OL,10,FUkrainian authorities reported an
OL,11,Fattack on the nearby port of Izmail.
OL,13,FRussia has not yet commented on the
OL,14,Fincident.
OL,16,FRomania is a member of Nato, a
OL,17,Ftransatlantic defence pact involving
OL,18,Fthe United States, which employs the
OL,19,Fprinciple that an attack on one is an
OL,20,Fattack on all.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1780095786
OL,3,CDrone hits Romanian apartment block as
OL,4,CNato condemns Russia's 'recklessness'
OL,6,FNato members have found themselves
OL,7,Fincreasingly responding to Russian
OL,8,Fdrones and missiles that have either
OL,9,Fentered their airspace or come down in
OL,10,Ftheir territory, ramping up tensions
OL,11,Fwith Moscow.
OL,13,FMark Rutte, Nato's secretary general,
OL,14,Fcondemned "Russia's reckless
OL,15,Fbehaviour" on Friday as "a danger to
OL,16,Fus all", assuring Romanian President
OL,17,FNicusor Dan that it "stands ready to
OL,18,Fdefend every inch of allied territory".
OL,26,@yD@E{y
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1780095786
OL,3,CDrone hits Romanian apartment block as
OL,4,CNato condemns Russia's 'recklessness'
OL,6,FEuropean Commission President Ursula
OL,7,Fvon der Leyen also said the incident
OL,8,Fshowed that Russia "has crossed yet
OL,9,Fanother line".
OL,11,FShe said the European Union will keep
OL,12,Fstrengthening security along its
OL,13,Feastern border and was actively
OL,14,Fdrafting another set of sanctions
OL,15,Fagainst Russia, the 21st so far.
OL,17,FEuropean countries were also swift to
OL,18,Fcondemn Russia.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1780095786
OL,3,CDrone hits Romanian apartment block as
OL,4,CNato condemns Russia's 'recklessness'
OL,6,FUK Foreign Secretary, Yvette Cooper,
OL,7,Fbranded Russia's violation of Nato
OL,8,Fairspace "extremely dangerous and
OL,9,Freckless".
OL,11,F"The UK strongly condemns this grave
OL,12,Fescalation that puts lives at risk,"
OL,13,Fshe wrote on X, adding: "The UK stands
OL,14,Funited with Romania and all Allies to
OL,15,Fdefend every inch of NATO territory."
OL,17,FEstonian Foreign Minister Margus
OL,18,FTsahkna said the risk of such "serious
OL,19,Fincidents" was raised by "Putin's
OL,20,Fincreasing nervousness, driven by
OL,21,Fmilitary setbacks".
OL,26,@zD@_OU{D@JO]{D@ZOU}D@RO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1780095786
OL,3,CDrone hits Romanian apartment block as
OL,4,CNato condemns Russia's 'recklessness'
OL,6,F"Russia is growing weaker on the
OL,7,Fbattlefield in its war against
OL,8,FUkraine, yet it continues to pursue
OL,9,Fits objectives through brutal drone
OL,10,Fand missile attacks," he said in a
OL,11,Fstatement.
OL,13,FFrance's Foreign Minister Jean-Noel
OL,14,FBarrot has summoned Russia's
OL,15,Fambassador and condemned the
OL,16,F"irresponsible act", telling public
OL,17,Fbroadcaster France Inter that Moscow
OL,18,Fhas "targeted a friendly country, an
OL,19,FEU and NATO member".
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@UO]xD@AOUzD@EOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
