PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1780095786
OL,3,CDrone hits Romanian apartment block as
OL,4,CNato condemns Russia's 'recklessness'
OL,6,FLatvian President Edgars Rinkevics
OL,7,Falso condemned the Russian drone
OL,8,Fstrike and said it "stands in full
OL,9,Fsolidarity with our ally Romania and
OL,10,Fis prepared to support appropriate
OL,11,Fmeasures to prevent such violations."
OL,13,FRussian drones have breached Romania's
OL,14,Fairspace 28 times since Moscow began
OL,15,Fattacking Kyiv's ports across the
OL,16,FDanube, Romania's defence ministry
OL,17,Fsaid on Friday.
OL,26,@pD@TOUsD@eO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/11
