OL,3,CDrone hits Romanian apartment block as
OL,4,CNato condemns Russia's 'recklessness'
OL,6,FIn September 2025, Nato fighter jets
OL,7,Fshot down multiple Russian drones that
OL,8,Fviolated Polish airspace during an
OL,9,Fattack on neighbouring Ukraine.
OL,11,FThe military alliance denounced Moscow
OL,12,Ffor "absolutely dangerous" behaviour
OL,13,Fthat ratcheted up tensions to a new
OL,14,Flevel.
OL,16,FDays after that incident, Romania
OL,17,Fcondemned Moscow's "irresponsible
OL,18,Factions" after alleging that a Russian
OL,19,Fdrone breached Romanian airspace
OL,20,Fduring an attack on Ukraine, prompting
OL,21,FBucharest to scramble fighter jets.
OL,26,@tD@EOUtD@ZO]yD@TOUzD@HO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/11
