OL,3,CDrone hits Romanian apartment block as
OL,4,CNato condemns Russia's 'recklessness'
OL,6,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FUkrainian President Volodymyr
OL,12,FZelenskyy said on Thursday he was
OL,13,Fpressing the United States to provide
OL,14,Fmore Patriot air defence missiles able
OL,15,Fto counter the Russian attacks.
OL,17,FHe warned that deliveries to Ukraine
OL,18,Fare falling dangerously short as the
OL,19,Fwar in Iran diverts and depletes US
OL,20,Fstocks.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
