PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1780095786
OL,3,CDrone hits Romanian apartment block as
OL,4,CNato condemns Russia's 'recklessness'
OL,6,F"I believe (the US) must act quicker.
OL,7,FWe are being very persistent,"
OL,8,FZelenskyy told reporters during a
OL,9,Fvisit to Sweden.
OL,11,FUnited Nations Secretary-General
OL,12,FAntonio Guterres warned the UN
OL,13,FSecurity Council that the escalation
OL,14,Fand intensification of attacks risk
OL,15,Fgetting out of control, with "unknown
OL,16,Fand unintended consequences."
OL,18,FHe said that more civilians have been
OL,19,Fkilled in the first four months of
OL,20,Fthis year than in the same period in
OL,21,Fthe past three years.
